                    <h1>Mobil Delvac&trade; Express Italy</h1>
                    <div style="margin-top:-20px;" class="layoutRow clrfix">
                        <div class="mc1column"><!-- googleoff: all -->
                            <script type="text/javascript">quickEditForm("0915881d812146b6", '/Content/Video_Categories',true,'../forms/LCWVideoLandingCategory','','819px','655px','Category Sections','','pencil.gif','210px');</script><!-- googleon: all -->
                            <div class="item clrfix">
                                <a xmlns="" target="_self" onclick="trackClick(this);" href="../UK-English-LCW/heavydutyoils_mobil-delvac-express-finland.aspx"></a>
                                <h3><a xmlns="" title="" target="_self" onclick="trackClick(this);" href="../UK-English-LCW/heavydutyoils_mobil-delvac-express-finland.aspx">also see the Mobil Delvac Express Finland video<span></span></a>
                                </h3>
                                <p xmlns="">Mobil Delvac Express is designed to offer a fast, easy, while-you-wait oil change and first-class maintenance service for heavy duty vehicles without an appointment.</p>
                                <p xmlns="">Truck drivers can be assured that their vehicle fluid checks will be undertaken by a technical expert, who can then discuss next steps and agree the work with them.&nbsp;</p>
                                <p xmlns="">The Mobil Delvac Express Program is part of ExxonMobil&rsquo;s ongoing support to truck drivers, providing an innovative service, which helps heavy duty and commercial truck drivers reduce costs and maintain optimum performance whilst on the road.</p>
                                <h2 xmlns="">
                                    <img src="../Shared-Images-LCW/article_150x150-mobil-delvac-express-workshop_eame.jpg" height="90" width="90" alt="Mobil Delvac Express Workshop" title="Mobil Delvac Express Workshop" align="left" border="0" hspace="0" class="imgFloatLeft"><br>
Case Study 1: Italy</h2>
                                <p xmlns="">This site was established in the Trento Interservice workshop (part of the Nordauto Group) and is authorised by Mercedes-Benz, DAF, Volvo Trucks, Mitsubishi, Setra, Omniplus and Goldhofer. It enjoys a strategic location for both combined transport and international transport in the Trento Interporto, along the Brenner Motorway.</p>
                                <p xmlns="">Mobil Delvac Express provides drivers with a quick, professional and courteous oil change service. Whilst the oil is changed, drivers can choose to relax in a well-equipped lounge complete with armchairs, satellite TV and PCs. They can even take a rest in one of the bedrooms. Alternatively, they might want to take the opportunity to have a shower, pop into the sauna or even exert themselves in the gym.</p>
                                <p xmlns="">Other facilities include a laundry, a shop stocking a range of essentials,<br>
a restaurant, bar and truck wash.</p>
                                <p xmlns="">Tommaso Vito, Lubricants Manager for Esso Italiana, says: &ldquo;It is a pilot project focused on both fleets and private owners, by which we strive to provide a rapid, guaranteed, quality service. It is a service that can optimise those who live and work on trucks: this is the meaning behind our collaboration with Interservice.&rdquo;</p>
                                <p xmlns="">This collaboration was also strongly desired by the Chairman of<br>
Interservice, Roberto Pizzinini.</p>
